main event: A lookout on a Great Lakes ore boat sighted three circular UFOs near Lake Michigan on October 25, 1958.
interesting points: The sighted objects were circular, about six inches in diameter,The objects moved very fast and erratically,One UFO came in at about 12:50 A.M.,The sighting was about 40 miles west of the Mackinac bridge,The report was submitted to the Air Force in 1963, long after the sighting.
witness description: lookout on a Great Lakes ore boat
